  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "F&B Supervisor",
  "description": "<p>We are looking for a passionate and experienced Restaurant Supervisor to join the team at our Italian restaurant.</p><p>If you love Italian food, value authentic hospitality, and are ready to take a leadership role in a warm and vibrant environment, we want to hear from you!</p><p><br /></p><p>⸻</p><p><br /></p><p>Key Responsibilities:</p><p>• Supervise daily front-of-house operations during service</p><p>• Ensure a warm and welcoming dining experience for all guests</p><p>• Manage reservations, guest requests, and resolve complaints professionally</p><p>• Coordinate staff shifts and assist in training new team members</p><p>• Communicate effectively with the kitchen and management</p><p>• Enforce hygiene and food safety standards </p><p>• Oversee opening and closing duties, including cash handling</p><p>• Motivate the team and lead with a positive and hands-on approach</p><p><br /></p><p>Requirements:</p><p>• At least 1 year in a supervisory or team leader role, preferably in Italian cuisine</p><p>• Strong leadership and interpersonal skills</p><p>• Excellent communication and problem-solving abilities</p><p>• Good understanding of food service operations and hygiene regulations</p><p>• Able to work on weekends and public holidays</p><p>• Fluent in English; Italian language skills are a bonus</p><p>• 6 day work week based on roster shift</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p>",
